    <h1>UG Campaigns</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A complete historical record of the Urban Guerrillas across eras of combat.</p>

    <section>
        <h2>⭐ Early Tactical Era (2002–2005)</h2>
        <p>The birth of UG tactics — small‑unit realism, teamwork, and gritty infantry combat.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>SOCOM: U.S. Navy SEALs (2002)</li>
            <li>SOCOM II: U.S. Navy SEALs (2003)</li>
            <li>Delta Force: Black Hawk Down (2003)</li>
            <li>Men of Valor (2004)</li>
            <li>GTA: Vice City (2002)</li>
            <li>GTA: San Andreas (2004)</li>
            <li>Operation Flashpoint: Elite (2005)</li>
            <li>Call of Duty 2 (2005)</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>⭐ Modern Warfare Era (2006–2013)</h2>
        <p>UG enters the age of advanced tech, urban warfare, and large‑scale multiplayer combat.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Ghost Recon: Advanced Warfighter (2006)</li>
            <li>Gears of War (2006)</li>
            <li>Medal of Honor: Airborne (2007)</li>
            <li>Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare (2007)</li>
            <li>GTA IV (2008)</li>
            <li>Call of Duty: World at War (2008)</li>
            <li>Gears of War 2 (2008)</li>
            <li>Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2 (2009)</li>
            <li>Battlefield 3 (2011)</li>
            <li>Gears of War 3 (2011)</li>
            <li>Arma 3 (2013)</li>
            <li>Battlefield 4 (2013)</li>
            <li>GTA V (2013)</li>
            <li>Gears of War: Judgment (2013)</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>⭐ Advanced Tactical Era (2014–2019)</h2>
        <p>UG transitions into massive open worlds, refined gunplay, and modern battlefield systems.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Elite Dangerous (2014)</li>
            <li>Battlefield Hardline (2015)</li>
            <li>Gears of War 4 (2016)</li>
            <li>Ghost Recon: Wildlands (2017)</li>
            <li>Call of Duty: WWII (2017)</li>
            <li>Battlefield V (2018)</li>
            <li>Gears 5 (2019)</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>⭐ Space & Frontier Era (2014–Present)</h2>
        <p>UG expands beyond Earth — long‑range operations, exploration, and interstellar combat.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Elite Dangerous (2014–Present)</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

